#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:0.5"
msgid "54. Anādariyasikkhāpada"
msgstr ""
"<hgroup><h1 id=\"Bu-Pc.54\">Monks’ Confession 54: the training rule on "
"disrespect</h1></hgroup>"

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.1"
msgid "Tena samayena buddho bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme."
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"nidana\">Origin story</h2>\n"
"<p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.54.1\">Bu-Pc.54.1</a><a class=\"pts-vp-en\""
" id=\"BD.2.393\">BD.2.393</a><a class=\"wt-pa\">1046</a>At one time the "
"Buddha was staying at Kosambī in Ghosita’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā channo anācāraṃ ācarati."
msgstr "At that time Venerable Channa was misbehaving."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.3"
msgid "Bhikkhū evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "The monks would tell him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.4"
msgid "“māvuso channa, evarūpaṃ akāsi."
msgstr "“Channa, don’t do that;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.5"
msgid "Netaṃ kappatī”ti."
msgstr "it’s not allowable,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.6"
msgid "So anādariyaṃ paṭicca karotiyeva."
msgstr "and he just did it again out of disrespect.</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.7"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1047</a>The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.8"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.9"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā channo anādariyaṃ karissatī”ti … pe …"
msgstr "“How can Venerable Channa act disrespectfully?” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.10"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, channa, anādariyaṃ karosī”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, Channa, that you are acting disrespectfully?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.11"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.12"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked him, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.13"
msgid "kathañhi nāma tvaṃ, moghapurisa, anādariyaṃ karissasi."
msgstr "Foolish man, how can you act disrespectfully?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.14"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisa, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.15"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p><b class="rule">
#. REF: sc3
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:1.16"
msgid "“Anādariye pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"pannatti\">Final ruling</h2>\n"
"<p class=\"rule\"><a class=\"wt-pa\">1048</a>‘If a monk is disrespectful, he "
"commits an offense entailing confession.’”</p>"

#. HTML: </b></p><p><b class="term">
#. REF: sc4
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.1.1"
msgid "Anādariyaṃ nāma"
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"pada\">Definitions</h2>\n"
"<p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.54.2\"></a><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-"
"Pc.54.2.1\">Bu-Pc.54.2.1</a><a class=\"wt-pa\""
">1049</a><term>Disrespectful</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.1.2"
msgid "dve anādariyāni—"
msgstr "<gloss>there are two kinds of disrespect:"

#. HTML: </b>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.1.3"
msgid "puggalānādariyañca dhammānādariyañca."
msgstr "disrespect for the person and disrespect for the rule."

#. HTML: </p><p><b class="term">
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.1.4"
msgid "Puggalānādariyaṃ nāma"
msgstr "<a class=\"wt-pa\">1050</a><term>Disrespect for the person</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.1.5"
msgid "upasampannena paññattena vuccamāno—"
msgstr ""
"<gloss>if, <a class=\"pts-vp-en\" id=\"BD.2.394\">BD.2.394</a> when he is "
"spoken to by one who is fully ordained about a rule that has been laid down, "
"he thinks,"

#. HTML: </b>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.1.6"
msgid ""
"“ayaṃ ukkhittako vā vambhito vā garahito vā, imassa vacanaṃ akataṃ "
"bhavissatī”ti anādariyaṃ karoti, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"“They have been ejected/they have been reproved/they have been censured; I "
"won’t do what they say,” and he acts disrespectfully, then he commits an "
"offense entailing confession.</gloss>"

#. HTML: </p><p><b class="term">
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.1.7"
msgid "Dhammānādariyaṃ nāma"
msgstr "<a class=\"wt-pa\">1051</a><term>Disrespect for the rule</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.1.8"
msgid "upasampannena paññattena vuccamāno—"
msgstr ""
"<gloss>if, when is spoken to by one who is fully ordained about a rule that "
"has been laid down, he thinks,"

#. HTML: </b>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.1.9"
msgid ""
"“kathāyaṃ nasseyya vā vinasseyya vā antaradhāyeyya vā”, taṃ vā na "
"sikkhitukāmo anādariyaṃ karoti, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"“What can be done so that this rule is lost/perishes/disappears,”or he does "
"not want to train in that rule, and he acts disrespectfully, then he commits "
"an offense entailing confession.</gloss></gloss></p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.2.1"
msgid "Upasampanne upasampannasaññī anādariyaṃ karoti, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"cakka\">Permutations</h2>\n"
"<p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.54.2.2\">Bu-Pc.54.2.2</a><a class=\"wt-pa\""
">1052</a>If the other person is fully ordained, and he perceives them as "
"fully ordained, and he acts disrespectfully, he commits an offense entailing "
"confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.2.2"
msgid "Upasampanne vematiko anādariyaṃ karoti, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"If the other person is fully ordained, but he is unsure if they are, and he "
"acts disrespectfully, he commits an offense entailing confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.2.3"
msgid "Upasampanne anupasampannasaññī anādariyaṃ karoti, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"If the other person is fully ordained, but he does not perceive them as "
"fully ordained, and he acts disrespectfully, he commits an offense entailing "
"confession.</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8, pts-vp-pli4.114
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.2.4"
msgid "Apaññattena vuccamāno—"
msgstr ""
"<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1053</a>If he is being spoken to about something that "
"has not been laid down—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.2.5"
msgid ""
"“idaṃ na sallekhāya na dhutatthāya na pāsādikatāya na apacayāya na "
"vīriyārambhāya saṃvattatī”ti anādariyaṃ karoti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"“This isn’t conducive to the erasing of defilements/to ascetic practices/to "
"being inspiring/to a reduction in things/to being energetic”—and he acts "
"disrespectfully, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.2.6"
msgid "Anupasampannena paññattena vā apaññattena vā vuccamāno—"
msgstr ""
"If he is being spoken to by one who is not fully ordained, whether or not it "
"has been laid down—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.2.7"
msgid ""
"“idaṃ na sallekhāya na dhutatthāya na pāsādikatāya na apacayāya na "
"vīriyārambhāya saṃvattatī”ti anādariyaṃ karoti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"“This isn’t conducive to the erasing of defilements/to ascetic practices/to "
"being inspiring/to a reduction in things/to being energetic”—and he acts "
"disrespectfully, <a class=\"pts-vp-pi\" id=\"Vin.4.114\">Vin.4.114</a> he "
"commits an offense of wrong conduct. </p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.2.8"
msgid "Anupasampanne upasampannasaññī āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1054</a>If the other person is not fully ordained, but "
"he perceives them as fully ordained, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.2.9"
msgid "Anupasampanne vematiko, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If the other person is not fully ordained, but he is unsure of it, he "
"commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.2.10"
msgid "Anupasampanne anupasampannasaññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If the other person is not fully ordained, and he does not perceive them as "
"fully ordained, he commits an offense of wrong conduct.</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.3.1"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"anapatti\">Non-offenses</h2>\n"
"<p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.54.2.3\">Bu-Pc.54.2.3</a><a class=\"pts-vp-"
"en\" id=\"BD.2.395\">BD.2.395</a><a class=\"wt-pa\">1055</a>There is no "
"offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.3.2"
msgid ""
"“evaṃ amhākaṃ ācariyānaṃ uggaho paripucchā”ti bhaṇati, ummattakassa, "
"ādikammikassāti."
msgstr ""
"if he says, “This is how we were taught and examined by our teachers;” if he "
"is insane; if he is the first offender.</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsutta">
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc54:2.3.3"
msgid "Anādariyasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
"<hr><p class=\"endsutta\"><a class=\"wt-pa\">1056</a>The fourth rule, the "
"training rule on disrespect, is finished.</p>"
